node.text:
An Oklahoma-based, self-professed “bad runner” who abandoned expectations of what she should and shouldn’t do and starting running half-marathons. And then full marathons.

Moving our bodies is everything. We asked a handful of real-life Recreationalists what #DoingThings means to them — and how endorphins truly do make us all happier. See more of Katie @thekritch.

We’re on a mission to get the world moving. For us, fitness has never been about performance. We hike steep trails and hula hoop in the backyard simply because moving our bodies makes us happy. This is #DoingThings :wink:

That’s why we’re kicking the year off with a lineup of endorphin-worthy events, classes, and challenges inspired by the values we’ve been about since the beginning. Head to outdoorvoices.com to start #DoingThings
